## What this service is

This is a recurring reporting service. The client receives a ready-to-send weekly deliverable under your brand. It is useful when you already manage websites and need simple proof that monitoring and maintenance work is happening.

## What this service is not

It is not a full SEO audit, not a keyword research tool, and not a replacement for analytics platforms. It is a repeatable weekly health report that helps agencies communicate operational website issues clearly.

